      "content": "i know there are people to call but it doesnt change the fact that they're still there. the bullying doesnt just stop because i talk to a stranger on a phone. it just feels like a cycle that never ends. like no matter what i do, the world is just gonna keep being this loud and mean. everything feels so heavy and hopeless... like i'm just trapped in a world that doesn't want me there.",
